725591f-a.title: Queens: 70th Street - 47th Avenue
725591f-a.text:
70th Street, east side, south from 47th to 48th Avenues,
showing St. Marys Roman Catholic Church, at the S.E. corner
oof 47th Avenue, and the parochial school at the N.E. corner
of 48th Avenue, near the Long Island Railroad embankment.
View 2 shows the parochial school.
P. L. Sperr  June 7, 1927
NO REPRODUCTIONS  Views 1,2
